title: The Mad Hatters #28 Sneak Preview: Ladies Night With "Off The Grid" Ryan!
description: With Sam out of town Ryan goes for it and host his own episode with two lady callers... The Ally Cat and from the "Moon Me" podcast, Dana Moon.  Please enjoy and thank you for your support!
